00:39:33.894 --> 00:39:36.900
hit if he or she shoots at
distance d.

00:39:36.900 --> 00:39:40.500
Everyone happy with that?
That's the only notation I'm

00:39:40.500 --> 00:39:42.664
going to use today.
And I'm going to make some

00:39:42.664 --> 00:39:45.000
assumptions about the nature of
this probability.

